[SN]TITLE[SN]
Rio Olympics 2016: Khasan Khalmurzaev wins Russia's second judo gold

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Khasan Khalmurzaev won a second judo gold of the Rio Games for Russia in the men's -81kg category.

