Khalmurzaev, who won European gold in April, beat American Travis Stevens with a well-timed ippon.
Sergiu Toma won the UAE's first Olympic judo medal, and their first medal of these Games, as he beat Italy's Matteo Marconcini to bronze.
Takanori Nagase secured a ninth bronze for Japan with victory over Georgian number one seed Avtandil Tchrikishvili.
